give you guys $250,000,

17:42.028 --> 17:44.030
but I want 25%
of the business.

17:46.566 --> 17:49.735
Ohh, your valuation
just got crushed.

17:49.835 --> 17:54.006
Okay. Thank you. Um...

17:54.106 --> 17:55.942
Would you do, um...?

17:56.042 --> 17:56.742
Oh, sorry.

17:58.044 --> 18:00.680
We could
go for...15%?

18:03.182 --> 18:06.485
How about 17.5%?

18:06.586 --> 18:08.788
Make it 20%, and you've
got yourself a deal.

18:11.557 --> 18:12.458
We got a deal!

18:14.193 --> 18:15.027
O'Leary: Wow.

18:15.127 --> 18:17.363
Oh, my gosh!
I love it.

18:17.463 --> 18:19.298
So amazing!
Thank you.

18:19.398 --> 18:21.801
Well done, guys. Amazing.
You look beautiful.

18:21.901 --> 18:23.069
Thank you.
Congrats, guys.

18:23.169 --> 18:24.470
- Thank you. Have a good one.
- Well done, well done.

18:24.570 --> 18:28.674
They're on to something.
They're on to an absolute winner.

18:28.774 --> 18:29.909
I told you.

18:30.009 --> 18:32.345
Ahh!
I cannot believe this!

18:32.445 --> 18:33.412
We did it!
We did!

18:33.512 --> 18:34.714
Congratulations!
I'm so happy!

18:34.814 --> 18:36.782
I love you so much.
Yay!

