In Season 13, we watched
Bo Haaber and Rasmus Barfred

18:43.456 --> 18:44.857
make a deal with
Robert Herjavec

18:44.957 --> 18:48.027
for their custom swim goggles
company, TheMagic5.

18:48.127 --> 18:50.296
I'll give you
$1 million for 6.5%.

18:50.396 --> 18:51.797
