19:30.636 --> 19:31.837
I did.
"Why don't you let me in?"

19:31.937 --> 19:34.674
Mark and his team have
provided strategic guidance

19:34.774 --> 19:36.175
all around the business.

19:36.275 --> 19:39.812
And Robert has
been focused on how to
get to new customers,

19:39.912 --> 19:41.881
especially online.

19:41.981 --> 19:43.816
With the success of
our swimming goggles,

19:43.916 --> 19:46.886
we are now moving
into other product areas.

19:46.986 --> 19:49.855
Virtual reality headsets
are very uncomfortable,

19:49.955 --> 19:51.490
so we have taken
our technology

19:51.590 --> 19:54.627
and enabled a custom fit
facial interface.

19:54.727 --> 19:57.463
This will make the headset
much more comfortable to wear,

19:57.563 --> 20:00.266
and you can wear your headset
for a longer time.

20:00.366 --> 20:03.769
We've also secured a
partnership with Canyon Bicycles.

20:03.869 --> 20:06.272
Canyon will be using
our customizing technology.

20:06.372 --> 20:08.808
That will enable the biker
to control the bike better,

20:08.908 --> 20:11.110
and at the same time,
be more comfortable.

20:11.210 --> 20:13.112
My advice for
an entrepreneur is,

20:13.212 --> 20:14.613
ask yourself
the difficult question--

20:14.714 --> 20:16.782
