and do you solve it

20:16.882 --> 20:19.385
in a way that makes sense
for the customer?

20:19.485 --> 20:22.254
These guys, when you talk
to them, they're all in.

20:22.354 --> 20:23.222
Yeah.
It's all they think about,

20:23.322 --> 20:24.457
how to make
swimmers better,

20:24.557 --> 20:25.591
how to make
goggles better.

20:25.691 --> 20:27.293
They're very single-minded
and very focused,

20:27.393 --> 20:28.761
